    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the analog era, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe inspection. The suspension retains its factory-intended geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and balanced weight distribution remain intact. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical fundamentals are dialed for the discerning driver.",
